N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 255.4 - Notifications and reports

State Regulations

Unless otherwise indicated in this Part, submission of
any notification, program, plan, letter of intent, procedure, or written or
telephonic report as required by any provision of this Part shall be to the
department. Notes
